Package: CondDensReg
Type: Package
Title: Conditional density regression for individual-level data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Alexander", "Fottner", role = "aut",
		            email = "alexander.fottner@uni-a.de"), 
			 person("Eva-Maria", "Maier", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
			        email = "eva-maria.maier@hu-berlin.de"),
			 person("Lea", "Runge", role = "aut", 
			        email = "lea.runge.1@hu-berlin.de"))
Maintainer: Eva-Maria Maier <eva-maria.maier@hu-berlin.de>
Description: Structured additive regression models for mixed densities as
    response and scalar covariates are fitted via Poisson regression models, where
    the continuous part of the density is approximated with histograms.
